description: Darling is desperate to pay her student loans for med school. She finds herself wrapped up with a mysterious man who's been paying her thousands of dollars for the rarest type of blood on the planet, Rh null. But why? Curiosity gets the best of her and she steals a sip for herself and is then compelled to follow him to his hideout where she discovers an underground sex cult fueled by blood! Rough gangbang sex, double penetration, bondage and bukkake all included! Not to be missed!
title: Bloodlust: Med student gangbanged and double penetrated by sex cult!
